---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayoutV2.astro';

const title = "Prescription Refill Request Tool – KindScript";
const description = "Create a clear, polite message to request a medication refill — for yourself or someone you’re supporting.";
const keywords = "prescription refill, refill request, medication letter, patient tool";
const author = "KindScript";
const date = "2025-08-06";
const lastUpdated = "2025-08-18";
---

<BaseLayout
  title={title}
  description={description}
  keywords={keywords}
  author={author}
  date={date}
  lastUpdated={lastUpdated}
>
  <div class="tool-page">
    <h1>💊 Prescription Refill Request Generator</h1>
    <p>A template to help you ask for a medication refill — clearly and respectfully — when you’re running low or need to explain why it’s important.</p>

    <h2>🔍 What this tool is</h2>
    <p>
      This tool helps you write a refill request you can send to your doctor, clinic, or care team. It’s helpful when you’re low on medication, switching providers, or facing an insurance delay.
    </p>
    <p>
      You can use it for yourself or to help a loved one. We’ll guide you through what to include — you don’t need perfect wording or medical terms.
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>🔒 <strong>Private by design</strong><br />Everything you write stays on your device. It’s never saved, sent, or tracked.</li>
      <li>🩺 <strong>Not medical advice</strong><br />This is a writing tool — not a prescription service or substitute for professional care.</li>
    </ul>

    <p>🛠️ Ready to begin? <a href="#refill-form">Jump to the form</a></p>

    <hr class="tool-divider">

    <h3>📝 Example output</h3>
    <pre class="output-box">Hi,

I'm writing to request a refill for Sertraline 50mg, which I’ve been taking for about 8 months. It’s been helpful in managing my anxiety symptoms, and I’m running low.

I have a follow-up appointment in two weeks but may run out before then.

Thanks so much,  
Jordan Reyes</pre>

<hr class="tool-divider">

    <div class="section tool-form" id="refill-form">
      <div class="form-inner">
        <form id="form">
          <label>
  Patient name:
  <input type="text" id="patientName" placeholder="e.g. Jordan Reyes" required>
</label>

<label>
  Medication name + dose:
  <input type="text" id="medication" placeholder="e.g. Sertraline 50mg" required>
</label>

<label>
  How long you’ve been taking it (optional):
  <input type="text" id="duration" placeholder="e.g. 8 months">
</label>

<label>
  Why you’re requesting a refill:
  <textarea id="reason" placeholder="e.g. I’m running low and this medication has helped manage my depression." required></textarea>
</label>

<label>
  Who the medication is for:
  <input type="text" id="forWhom" placeholder="e.g. Myself, My mother (Lisa), My child (Max)">
</label>

<label>
  Anything else they should know (optional):
  <textarea id="extraInfo" placeholder="e.g. I have an appointment in 2 weeks but may run out before then."></textarea>
</label>

          <div class="form-action-area">
            <button type="button" id="generate-btn" class="btn dark">✨ Generate Refill Request</button>
          </div>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>

    <hr class="tool-divider">

    <h2>📋 Generated Request</h2>
    <p>You can copy, print, or share this message — whatever works best.</p>
    <div id="refillOutput" class="output-box" contenteditable="true" role="textbox" aria-label="Generated refill request">
      (Fill out the form and click Generate)
    </div>

    <div class="button-group">
      <button id="copy-btn" class="btn dark">Copy to Clipboard</button>
      <button id="print-btn" class="btn dark">Print This</button>
      <button id="download-btn" class="btn dark">Download as .txt</button>
    </div>
  </div>
   <hr class="tool-divider">
  <p style="font-size: 0.875rem; text-align: center; margin-top: 2rem;">
  📌 Want to get the most out of this tool? Visit <a href="/how-to-use">How to Use KindScript</a>.
</p>

  <div style="margin-top: 2rem;">
    <a href="/tools">← Back to all tools</a>
  </div>

  <script src="/js/refill-request.js" defer></script>
</BaseLayout>
